### Get all projects grouped by tenants (Main endpoint)
GET {{host}}/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get all projects grouped by tenants (Explicit endpoint)
GET {{host}}/api/projects/by-tenants
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get simple list of projects (Backward compatibility)
GET {{host}}/api/projects/simple
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Variables for testing
@host = https://localhost:7253
@authToken = your-jwt-token-here

